item.description:
This meetup is for advanced players only. I'll set up nets ~ 6pm and we'll play til it gets dark.

See http://volleyball.mee... for description of levels.
Briefly, if you aren't comfortable with 5-1 or 6-2, if you aren't comfortable hitting or setting 2s, shoots, or the occasional 1, this is probably not the level for you. In order to maintain a quality game, you may be asked to leave if your level of play is not sufficient.
item.name: ADVANCED Outdoor Volleyball Mon 7/20 6pm Sydney & Pacific
